<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Business Compliance Services - Greymatter Accountancy</title>
  <link class="stylesheet" rel="stylesheet" href="../css/styles.css">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Sora:wght@400;600;700&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body>
  <%- include('partials/header', { rootPath: '../' , currentPage: 'page' }) %>

    <section class="page-header page-header-light">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Business Compliance Services</h1>
        <p>Professional, reliable compliance reporting to keep your UK business on solid footing with HMRC and Companies
          House.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="services-detail services-page">
      <div class="container">

        <div class="services-grid" style="margin-bottom: 40px;">

          <!-- Bookkeeping -->
          <div class="service-detail-card">
            <div class="service-detail-header">
              <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-book"></i></div>
              <h2>Bookkeeping</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="service-detail-content">
              <p>Accurate, real-time records are the foundation of healthy business decisions. We maintain your ledgers
                on daily,
                weekly, or monthly basis, ensuring that your accounts are always up-to-date, organized and audit-ready.
              </p>
              <h3>What we cover:</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Sales and purchase ledger updates</li>
                <li>Bank, credit card, and loan reconciliations</li>
                <li>Receipt processing via cloud-based tools such as Dext, Hubdoc</li>
                <li>Monthly management reporting support</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Statutory Accounts -->
          <div class="service-detail-card">
            <div class="service-detail-header">
              <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-shield-halved"></i></div>
              <h2>Statutory Accounts</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="service-detail-content">
              <p>Year-end statutory accounts prepared in accordance with UK GAAP/FRS with filling submitted to and filed
                to Companies House and HMRC, as required.</p>
              <h3>What we cover:</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Preparation of Balance Sheets and Profit & Loss Accounts</li>
                <li>Preparation of statutory notes and directors' reports</li>
                <li>Reconciliation of balance sheet control accounts</li>
                <li>E-filing of statutory accounts with companies House</li>
                <li>Review of Year-end adjustments and accounting disclosures</li>

              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Payroll & Pensions -->
          <div class="service-detail-card">
            <div class="service-detail-header">
              <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-people-carry-box"></i></div>
              <h2>Payroll & Pensions</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="service-detail-content">
              <p>Pay your team correctly, securely, and on time. We handle the complete monthly or weekly payroll bureau
                cycle, including pension compliance.</p>
              <h3>What we cover:</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Real Time Information (RTI) submissions to HMRC</li>
                <li>Custom payslip generation and distribution</li>
                <li>Auto-enrolment workplace pension compliance (NEST, etc.)</li>
                <li>P60s, P45s, and student loan deduction management</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- VAT Returns -->
          <div class="service-detail-card">
            <div class="service-detail-header">
              <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-receipt"></i></div>
              <h2>VAT Returns</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="service-detail-content">
              <p>Stay aligned with Making Tax Digital (MTD) rules. We compute, double-check, and file your VAT returns,
                choosing the most optimal schemes.</p>
              <h3>What we cover:</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>VAT return preparation and MTD-compliant filing</li>
                <li>Scheme assessment (Cash, Accrual, Flat Rate, Annual)</li>
                <li>Partial exemption calculations and advice</li>
                <li>HMRC VAT audit representation and queries</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Making Tax Digital -->
          <div class="service-detail-card">
            <div class="service-detail-header">
              <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-cloud-arrow-up"></i></div>
              <h2>Making Tax Digital</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="service-detail-content">
              <p>Fully transition your business to HMRC's digital mandate. We implement compliant systems and ensure
                your digital links satisfy HMRC regulations.</p>
              <h3>What we cover:</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>MTD software readiness and setup</li>
                <li>Digital link verification across software platforms</li>
                <li>MTD for VAT compliance audits</li>
                <li>Preparation and advice for MTD for Income Tax Self Assessment (ITSA)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Corp Tax -->
          <div class="service-detail-card">
            <div class="service-detail-header">
              <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-percent"></i></div>
              <h2>Corporation Tax</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="service-detail-content">
              <p>Ensure your company files accurate CT600 returns. We analyse your expenses and capital expenditure to
                optimise tax reliefs and allowances, while ensuring full compliace with HMRC requirements.</p>
              <h3>What we cover:</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Corporation Tax computation and CT600 preparation</li>
                <li>Capital allowances reviews adn claims preperaion, including Annual Investments (AIA)
                </li>
                <li>R&D tax relief review anc laims</li>
                <li>Annual installment payment plans if applicable</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Secretarial & HMRC -->
          <div class="service-detail-card">
            <div class="service-detail-header">
              <div class="service-detail-icon"><i class="fas fa-file-contract"></i></div>
              <h2>Secretarial & HMRC</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="service-detail-content">
              <p>Handle corporate administration without the stress. We act as your company secretarial department and
                manage all formal correspondence with HMRC.</p>
              <h3>What we cover:</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Annual Confirmation Statement filing</li>
                <li>Registered Office and Director details management</li>
                <li>Resolving HMRC compliance and billing discrepancies</li>
                <li>Share transfer forms and dividend declarations</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="cta-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Need Comprehensive Business Compliance?</h2>
        <p>Let's design a structured compliance package for your company.</p>
        <a href="../index.html#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Book a Consultation</a>
      </div>
    </section>
    <%- include('partials/footer', { rootPath: '../' , currentPage: 'page' }) %>
</body>

</html>